subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which king established the Chittor Fort?
question_hi: चिट्टोर किस राज्य के राजनीतिक विभिन्न क्या इसके संस्करण कलाई?
A_hi: राजनीतिक विभिन्न राजन किसे क्या कलाई?
explanation: King Rao Jodha established the city of Bundi in Rajasthan. He is often considered as the author of the famous Chittorgarh Treaty in 1559.
